Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BUNDALL CORPORATE OFFICE BUILDING FOR LEASE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This three level office building is centrally located in Bundall CBD and is within close proximity to Gold Coast City Council's Headquarters.

- 235 sqm
- Fitout includes reception, boardroom, kitchen/meeting room, two offices, server room and open plan area
- Entitled to six parking bays at asking rate

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please  contact the agent via the above links.

Bundall's Corporate Centre precinct is the Gold Coast's premier office park environment comprising of two iconic towers: Corporate Centre One and Wyndham Corporate Centre. Located on a high profile corner position and are the Gold Coast's most recognised office buildings attracting a strong mix of international, national and local tenants.

The precinct has exceptional accessibility which is unrivalled in the coastal CBD centres following the recent upgrade of Bundall Road / Ferry Road to six lanes from Broadbeach to Southport.

The Corporate Centre Precinct offers plenty of staff amenities including a lobby cafe and restaurant/cafe, as well as the EMF health club which includes a full range of gym equipment and facilities, including a 25 metre heated pool and special rates for occupants. The urban village of Chevron Island is less than a five minute walk with access to banks, restaurants, cafes and bars along with the 150 Public House and Gold Coast Cultural Precinct located across the waterway.

All availabilities present as a very high standard along with high quality finishes throughout, including lift lobby areas and common area facilities.


Wyndham Corporate Centre:
- A 11 level A-grade office tower with all floors serviced by three lifts
- Availability from 382sqm to 1,042sqm fully floors
- 3,116sqm of contiguous space over 3 floors (approximately)
- Secure basement parking and additional staff parking on-site
- Two hour visitor parking - free of charge
- 5-star NABERS Energy Rating

Corporate Centre One:
- A 16 level A-grade office tower with marble clad ground floor lift lobby, providing a magnificent entry statement with all floors serviced by four lifts and all tenancies enjoying sweeping Gold Coast views
- Availability from 68 sqm and up to 690 sqm (approximately)
- Secure basement parking and additional staff parking on-site
- Two hour visitor parking - free of charge
- 4.5-star NABERS Energy Rating


The Corporate Centre Precinct offers a range of options for businesses of all sizes along with a wide range of flexible lease packages, including turnkey fitout and fully furnished options.

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive agent via the links above.
